<!--
  ribbon.xml — custom ribbon page for HW 2025.1+ (compat/hv2025.1).

  Adds one new top-level ribbon tab "HV Tools" with a single button
  that opens HVTools_Panel.tcl (the combined Max Stress + Safety
  Factor panel). Schema per Altair's official "Ribbons XML" reference
  (actionlist/spriteaction + page/group/actiongroup) — CONFIRMED
  working on a real 2025.1 install 2026-07-16 (the "HV Tools" tab
  appeared correctly after the extension.xml profile-nesting fix).

  Fixed: the "Launch" actiongroup first rendered as an empty box with
  no visible button; fixed by adding image="hvtools_icon.png" below,
  paired with extension.xml's resources="images" entry (matches
  Altair's own Extension Demo convention).

  REVERTED 2026-07-16: button rendered fine but clicking did nothing,
  so a more complex command (guard + catch + tk_messageBox) was tried
  together with a duplicate per-profile tclscript entry in
  extension.xml — that combination crashed HW on the real 2025.1
  install. Reverted the command back to this simple, confirmed-non-
  crashing one-liner to isolate which change was actually responsible
  before retrying either piece separately.

  This file lives FLAT alongside HVTools_Panel.tcl and the other 15
  deploy files (same folder as everything else in the zip) — NOT in a
  subfolder. Register the whole deploy folder itself via File >
  Extensions > Add Extension in HyperWorks (browse to the FOLDER, not
  to extension.xml directly) — NOT via "Import ribbon from XML" /
  "Import Custom Pages", which is a different, unrelated GUI feature
  that doesn't read extension.xml or run global-init.tcl at all.
-->
<root>
  <actionlist>
    <spriteaction tag="HVTools_Open" text="HV Tools Panel"
      tooltip="Open the HV Tools Panel (Max Stress sweep + Safety Factor)"
      image="hvtools_icon.png"
      command="tcl: source [file join $::HVToolsExtDir HVTools_Panel.tcl]"/>
  </actionlist>

  <page tag="HVTools_Page" text="HV Tools">
    <group tag="HVTools_G" text="Panel">
      <actiongroup tag="HVTools_AG" text="Launch">
        <spriteaction actiontag="HVTools_Open"/>
      </actiongroup>
    </group>
  </page>
</root>
